HTML template management system for Dora blockchain explorer with embedded filesystem, caching, and minification.

## Architecture Patterns
- Use Go embed.FS for compile-time template embedding via `//go:embed *` directive
- Implement thread-safe template caching with RWMutex for production performance
- Support debug mode with live file reloading that bypasses cache
- Template names must be unique across entire directory structure

## Integration Requirements
- Templates must be compatible with utils.GetTemplateFuncs() function map
- Use parseTemplateFiles() for consistent template parsing across debug/production modes
- Minification is configurable via utils.Config.Frontend.Minify flag
- All templates must be parseable at compile-time for validation

## Template Organization
- Group related templates in subdirectories by functional area
- Use layout.html as base template for consistent page structure
- Include error templates (404.html, 500.html) in _layout directory
- SVG templates go in _svg directory for reusable components